XBMC Fargo Addon
----------------
To import the data from XBMC to Fargo you need to install the Fargo addon in XBMC.
Use this zip in the repo to install it.

Configure Fargo Addon
---------------------
Fill in the Fargo web site address. This is the address (url) where Fargo is hosted.
Click "Export Web Site Address to config file." and you're done.

i.e.:
Web Site Address: fargo.qzofp.nl
Export Web Site Address to config file.